<center><h1>HelloWorld.java</h1></center><p><br>

Below is the syntax highlighted version of <a href="https://introcs.cs.princeton.edu/java/11hello/HelloWorld.java">HelloWorld.java</a>
from <a href="https://introcs.cs.princeton.edu/java/11hello">§1.1 Hello World</a>.
</p><p><br>

